{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-post-container-index-tsx","path":"/astee/image-segmentation/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n_FDGMr4MxE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">[꼼꼼한 논문 설명] U-Net: Convolutional Networks for Biomedical Image Segmentation (MICCAI 2015)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://youtube.com/watch?v=sbcC6N5xfy8&#x26;feature=shares\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">이미지 세그멘테이션 Image Segmentation 한번에 끝내기</a></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2>Semantic Segmentation</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>분할(Segmentation)에서는 <em>각 픽셀마다</em> 하나의 클래스로 분류함</li>\n<li>이미지가 주어졌을 때, <em>(높이 X 너비 X 1)</em> 크기를 가지는 <em>한 장의 분할 맵(Segmentation map)</em> 을 생성한다.\n<img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/corinthionia/post/14361149-283d-4431-b724-0278003467ae/image.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>목표</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>각 픽셀마다 N개의 클래스에 대한 확률을 뱉어야 하므로, 정답은 <em>(높이 X 너비 X N)</em> 의 형태를 갖는다.</li>\n<li>각 픽셀마다 <em>원-핫 인코딩(one-hot encoding)</em> 형식을 따른다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>모델 학습</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>분할(Segmentation) 작업을 위한 데이터셋 생성 비용은 매우 비싸다 -> 각 픽셀마다 어떤 클래스로 분류되는지 일일이 지정해야 하기 때문이다.)</li>\n<li>하지만 일반적인 CNN 분류 모델의 형식을 크게 바꾸지 않고 학습할 수 있다 -> 딥러닝 네트워크 구조가 어렵지 않다! 객체 탐지 분야의 네트워크 구조가 오히려 더 복잡한 편이다!</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>U-Net</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>U-Net 아키텍처는 U자형으로 생긴 네트워크이다.</li>\n<li>수축경로(Contracting path): 이미지에 존재하는 넓은 문맥(Context) 정보를 처리한다.</li>\n<li>확장경로(Expanding path): 정밀한 지역화(Precise loaclization)이 가능하도록 한다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Convolution 연산의 종류</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Down-sampling 목적: Strided Convolution - 너비와 높이가 감소(해상도 감소!)</li>\n<li>Up-sampling 목적: Transposed Convolution - 너비와 높이가 증가(해상도 증가!)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>U-Net Architecture</h2>\n<p><img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/corinthionia/post/1fff7989-1321-4f69-8193-b8071f6259a8/image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h3>수축 경로(Contracting Path)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>U-Net 아키텍처의 초반 부분</li>\n<li>2 * 2 Max pooling 사용 - 해상도(너비와 높이) <strong>2배 감소</strong></li>\n<li>Conv 연산으로 채널 크기는 2배 증가</li>\n<li>일반적인 CNN 모델처럼 다음의 형식을 반복: Conv 연산들 -> ReLU -> Max pooling</li>\n<li>그래서 사실 U-Net의 인코더 부분에 이미 학습이 잘되어 있는 다른 분류 모델을 사용하는 경우도 많다</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>확장 경로(Expansive Path)</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>U-Net 아키텍처의 후반 부분</li>\n<li>2 * 2 Convolution (Up-convolution) 사용 - 해상도(너비와 높이)가 <strong>2배 증가</strong></li>\n<li>Conv 연산으로 채널 크기는 2배 감소</li>\n<li>수축 경로에서 처리된 feature 채널 레벨에서 연결(concatenation) map을 잘라내어 가져와 수행</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>U-Net의 Overlap-tile 전략</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>FCN 특성상 입력 이미지의 해상도에는 제한이 없다. 하지만 <strong>U-Net 구조상 출력 이미지의 해상도가 입력 이미지보다 작다!</strong></li>\n<li>따라서 실제 필요한 영역보다 큰 범위의 패치를 삽입해서 결과를 뽑은 뒤, 그것을 출력 결과 패치로써 사용한다.</li>\n<li>이미지의 경계 부분은 Extrapolation을 사용한다 - 미러링(Mirroring) 활용\n<img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/corinthionia/post/64d34249-d969-4750-bc41-d3912e514fc1/image.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>U-Net의 학습 방법: Objective Function</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>U-Net은 Segmentation을 위한 네트워크이므로, 픽셀 단위로 소프트맥스를 사용한다.\n<img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/corinthionia/post/82ffc7f9-607f-4aa2-88e6-6d2652ef68a0/image.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n<li>학습을 위해 다음의 cross-entropy 손실을 사용한다. (true label만 고려하므로 일반 cross entropy 공식과 동일)\n<img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/corinthionia/post/0723dc74-d04a-484a-b25c-6e59e570381a/image.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n<li>세포(Cell)를 명확히 구분하기 위해 작은 분리 경계(Small separation border)를 학습한다.\n<img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/corinthionia/post/b6c060a7-c0c9-486d-a845-9133080e1992/image.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>U-Net의 데이터 증진 (Data Augmentation)</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>의료 데이터에서는 학습 데이터의 수가 적은 경우가 많으므로, 데이터 증진이 필요하다.</li>\n<li>추가적으로 Elastic Deformation 방법을 사용할 수 있다. (아래 사진 참고)\n<img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/corinthionia/post/5c9c698f-0194-4a57-a3ca-611631be4d8c/image.png\" alt=\"\"></li>\n</ul>\n<br/>\n<h1>실습</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.robots.ox.ac.uk/~vgg/data/pets/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">The Oxford-IIIT Pet Dataset</a></li>\n<li>Tensorflow</li>\n<li>Google Colab</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>1. 데이터셋 다운받기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">!curl <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>OL https<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">//</span>www<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>robots<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ox<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ac<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>uk<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">~</span>vgg<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>data<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>pets<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>data<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>images<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>tar<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>gz\n!curl <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>OL https<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">//</span>www<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>robots<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ox<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ac<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>uk<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">~</span>vgg<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>data<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>pets<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>data<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>annotations<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>tar<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>gz\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 압축 해제</span>\n!tar <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>xf images<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>tar<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>gz\n!tar <span class=\"token operator\">-</span>xf annotations<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>tar<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>gz</code></pre></div>\n<h3>2. 데이터셋의 이미지 확인하기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> os\n\ninput_dir <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'images'</span>\ntarget_dir <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'annotations/trimaps'</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># annotation 한 결과</span>\nimg_size <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">160</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">160</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># 이 크기로 구성되어 있음</span>\nnum_classes <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span>\nbatch_size <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">32</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># hyper parameter</span>\n\ninput_img_paths <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">sorted</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>os<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>path<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>join<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>input_dir<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> fname<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n                        <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> fname <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> os<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>listdir<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>input_dir<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n                            <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> fname<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>endswith<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'.jpg'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\ntarget_img_paths <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">sorted</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>os<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>path<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>join<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>target_dir<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> fname<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n                        <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> fname <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> os<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>listdir<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>target_dir<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n                            <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> fname<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>endswith<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">and</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">not</span> fname<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>startswith<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 자주 사용하는 이미지 라이브러리들 사용</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> IPython<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>display <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> Image<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> display\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> tensorflow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>keras<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>preprocessing<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>image <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> load_img\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> PIL\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> PIL <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> ImageOps\n\ndisplay<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Image<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>filename<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>input_img_paths<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">20</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nimg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> PIL<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ImageOps<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>autocontrast<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>load_img<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>target_img_paths<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">20</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\ndisplay<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>img<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>그러면 실행 결과로 다음과 같은 이미지를 확인할 수 있다. 위의 사진이 원본 이미지이고, 아래 사진이 우리가 맞혀야 하는 ‘정답’에 해당하는 사진이다.\n<img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/corinthionia/post/a5d5da44-820b-4fe8-8f56-c27067760f32/image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<h3>3. 데이터 전처리</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> numpy <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> np\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> tensorflow <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> keras\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">OxfordPets</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>keras<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>utils<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Sequence<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">__init__</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> batch_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> img_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> input_img_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> target_img_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>batch_size <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> batch_size\n    self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>img_size <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> img_size\n    self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>input_img_path <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> input_img_paths\n    self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target_img_path <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> target_img_paths\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">__len__</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">len</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target_img_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">//</span> self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>batch_size\n\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">__getitem__</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> idx<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token comment\"># 가져올 때 batch 단위로 가져오기 때문에 다음의 과정이 필요함!</span>\n    i <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> idx <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>batch_size\n    batch_input_img_path <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>input_img_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>batch_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    batch_target_img_path <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>target_img_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> i <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>batch_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\"># input 이미지들을 batch 단위로 x에 넣음</span>\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>zeros<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>batch_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>img_size <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> dtype<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'float32'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> j<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> path <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">enumerate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>batch_input_img_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      img <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> load_img<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>path<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> target_size<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>img_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n      x<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> img\n\n    y <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>zeros<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>batch_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>img_size <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> dtype<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"uint8\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> j<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> path <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">enumerate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>batch_target_img_path<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n      img <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> load_img<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>path<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> target_size<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>img_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> color_mode<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"grayscale\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n      y<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>expand_dims<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>img<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n      y<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>j<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>  <span class=\"token comment\"># 0, 1, 2, ... 로 label하기 위함</span>\n\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> y</code></pre></div>\n<h3>4. Validation에 사용할 데이터 추출</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> random\n\n<span class=\"token comment\"># validation에 사용할 1000개의 데이터 랜덤 추출</span>\nval_samples <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000</span>\nrandom<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Random<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1337</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>shuffle<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>input_img_paths<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nrandom<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Random<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1337</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>shuffle<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>target_img_paths<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\ntrain_input_img_paths <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> input_img_paths<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>val_samples<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\ntrain_target_img_paths <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> target_img_paths<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>val_samples<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\nval_input_img_paths <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> input_img_paths<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>val_samples<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\nval_target_img_paths <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> target_img_paths<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span>val_samples<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\ntrain_gen <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> OxfordPets<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>batch_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> img_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> train_input_img_paths<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> train_target_img_paths<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nval_gen <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> OxfordPets<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>batch_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> img_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> val_input_img_paths<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> val_target_img_paths<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>5. 모델 구성 - Down sampling &#x26; Up sampling</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> tensorflow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>keras <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> layers\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">get_model</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>img_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> num_classes<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  inputs <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> keras<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Input<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>shape<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>img_size <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Conv2D<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">32</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> strides<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> padding<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'same'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>inputs<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>BatchNormalization<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Activation<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'relu'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  previous_block_activation <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> x\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\"># Down sampling</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> filters <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">64</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">128</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">256</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Activation<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'relu'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>SeparableConv2D<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>filters<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> padding<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'same'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>BatchNormalization<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Activation<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'relu'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>SeparableConv2D<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>filters<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> padding<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'same'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>BatchNormalization<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>MaxPooling2D<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> strides<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> padding<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'same'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n    residual <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Conv2D<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>filters<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> strides<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> padding<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'same'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>previous_block_activation<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>add<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> residual<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    previous_block_activation <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> x\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\"># Up sampling</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> filters <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">256</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">128</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">64</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">32</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Activation<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'relu'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Conv2DTranspose<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>filters<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> padding<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'same'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>BatchNormalization<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Activation<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'relu'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Conv2DTranspose<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>filters<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> padding<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'same'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>BatchNormalization<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>UpSampling2D<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n    residual <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>UpSampling2D<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>previous_block_activation<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    residual <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Conv2D<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>filters<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> padding<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'same'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>residual<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>add<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> residual<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    previous_block_activation <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> x\n\n  outputs <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> layers<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Conv2D<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>num_classes<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> activation<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'softmax'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> padding<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'same'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n  model <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> keras<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Model<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>inputs<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> outputs<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> model\n\nmodel <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> get_model<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>img_size<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> num_classes<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nmodel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>summary<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>6. 모델 학습</h3>\n<p>에포크를 20으로 설정했는데 20분이 넘게 걸렸다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">model<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token builtin\">compile</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>optimizer<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'rmsprop'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> loss<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">'sparse_categorical_crossentropy'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\ncallbacks <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>keras<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>callbacks<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ModelCheckpoint<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'oxford_segmentation.h5'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> save_best_only<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token boolean\">True</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n\nepochs <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">20</span>\nmodel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>fit<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>train_gen<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> epochs<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>epochs<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> validation_data<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>val_gen<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> callbacks<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>callbacks<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>7. 추론</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">val_preds <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> model<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>predict<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>val_gen<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">display_mask</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  mask <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>argmax<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>val_preds<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> axis<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  mask <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> np<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>expand_dims<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mask<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> axis<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  img <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> PIL<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ImageOps<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>autocontrast<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>keras<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>preprocessing<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>image<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>array_to_img<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mask<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  display<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>img<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\ni <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">20</span>\n\ndisplay<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Image<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>filename<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>val_input_img_paths<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nimg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> PIL<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ImageOps<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>autocontrast<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>load_img<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>val_target_img_paths<span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\ndisplay<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>img<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\ndisplay_mask<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>i<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/corinthionia/post/2d590af7-21ad-42a5-97c9-ac9c8d4d023c/image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://velog.velcdn.com/images/corinthionia/post/0dc812b1-4e53-49e2-ae0c-2329cc5bd3bb/image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>순서대로 원본 이미지, 정답에 해당하는 이미지, 결과로 출력된 이미지이다.</p>\n<hr>\n<h2>Reference</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n_FDGMr4MxE\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">[꼼꼼한 논문 설명] U-Net: Convolutional Networks for Biomedical Image Segmentation (MICCAI 2015)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://youtube.com/watch?v=sbcC6N5xfy8&#x26;feature=shares\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">이미지 세그멘테이션 Image Segmentation 한번에 끝내기</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Image Segmentation [U-Net]","summary":"졸업 프로젝트 개발에 필요한 Image Segmentation 기술을 알아보고, 대표적인 U-Net 아키텍처에 대해 알아보자!","date":"January 17, 2023","categories":["astee"]}}}]},"file":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/bbf83/profile-image.jpg","srcSet":"/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/a8e5a/profile-image.jpg 30w,\n/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/bea51/profile-image.jpg 60w,\n/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/bbf83/profile-image.jpg 120w,\n/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/7793c/profile-image.jpg 240w","sizes":"(min-width: 120px) 120px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/2b147/profile-image.webp 30w,\n/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/caa3b/profile-image.webp 60w,\n/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/b15f9/profile-image.webp 120w,\n/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/b5014/profile-image.webp 240w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 120px) 120px, 100vw"}]},"width":120,"height":120}},"publicURL":"/static/d52180935121e403984f48239a23e1b1/profile-image.jpg"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/astee/image-segmentation/"}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}